Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for a new submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent in 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' status across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time for cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the end of case where activity 'Payment Handled occurs

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for a new submission
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time from first 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to final 'Payment Handled' in cases where re-submission occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Total time for all activities to be completed after 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' after 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' before successful payment
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time for a case to be closed after 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the end of case where activity 'Payment Handled occurs

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in re-submitted cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' in cases that are successfully re-submitted and approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
